      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"5. FORGERY placed last time (30.75) at Angle Park in a Grade 6, finishing second and beaten 2.25 lengths. Has already won out of this draw. Looks suited and should go close. 7. DURAN PANTERA lines up chasing another win after scoring over 530m at Angle Park in 30.86, set up by a fast early sectional. Has good speed and will be prominent from out wide. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. 2. ASTER BALLISTIC is having first try over this longer journey. Missed the frame last time when 5th and beaten 9 lengths (23.22) at Murray Bridge. Looks a key chance on best figures. 4. REFERENT POWER placed last start at this track and distance and is in the mix again.\",\"runners\":[5,7,2,4],\"exclusive\":false}",
